{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1698-05_175","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"Eloge de la Santé","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", mai 1698 [tome 5], p. 175-178.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Ces Vers qui marquent si bien les premiers plaisirs qu’on goûte au Printemps, donnent lieu de souhaiter que cette belle saison durast toujours ; mais quel avantage pourroit-on tirer de ce qu’elle a de plus agreable, si on manquoit du plus grand des biens ? Il consiste en la Santé, dont vous allez entendre l’Eloge.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"label":{"value":"ELOGE DE LA SANTÉ.","id":"/div/quote/label"},"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"O Charmante Santé,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Que ta presence aimable","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Est un bien desirable ?","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quelle felicité","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De t’avoir pour partage","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En tout temps, en tout âge ?","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Est-il d’autre bonheur","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans le cours de la vie","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui doive faire envie,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et chatoüiller le cœur ?","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le luxe, l’abondance,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le sçavoir, l’éloquence,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les amours, les honneurs,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le brillant des grandeurs,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et la faveur des Princes,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sont des presens bien minces.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un monceau de tresors,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Une grande lignée,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et la beauté du corps","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’une Femme bien née,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[19]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ont-ils des biens sans toy ?","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[20]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quand ce seroit un Roy,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[21]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si la douleur l’accable,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[22]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je le tiens miserable ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[23]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et les bienfaits divers","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[24]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’accorde à la nature","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[25]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Auteur de l’Univers,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[26]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La charmante verdure","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[27]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui renaist tous les ans","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[28]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Au retour du Printemps,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[29]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce qu’il produit de rare","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[30]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour recréer nos sens,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[31]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout ce qui les répare","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[32]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quand ils sont languissans,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[33]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et ce que sa largesse","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[34]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Répand sur nous sans cesse,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[35]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Peut-il estre compté","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[36]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Comme un bien desirable,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[37]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans ta presence aimable,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[38]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"O charmante Santé.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[39]/#"}}]}}}}